Is there a push to blur the separation of church and state? Join MacKenzie Drebit and Matthew Schanche in Truth Matters as we delve into the impact of Sunday legislation on Christianity. Uncover Jesuit writings challenging this separation and influencing the narrative, promoting Sunday worship over the seventh-day Sabbath as foreseen in Revelation 13.

Learn about the United Nations' Universal Declaration of Human Rights and its potential to overrule protections in the Bill of Rights. Join Truth Matters as we uncover Bible prophecies reflected in current events!
